author: The Current
description:
Soul Asylum plays "Freak Accident" live at The Current
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube

Back in November, rock icons Soul Asylum, stopped by The Current studio to perform songs from their 13th studio record, Slowly but Shirley. Watch a performance of "Freak Accident" above.

Musicians
David Pirner – vocals, guitar
Ryan Smith – guitar, backing vocals
